      "id": "entry-001",
      "title": "Core Loop",
      "content": "## The Roguelike Deckbuilder Core Loop\n\nEchoes of the Void follows a familiar but refined roguelike deckbuilder structure:\n\n1. **Run Start** - Player begins with a starter deck of 10 basic Memory cards\n2. **Sector Navigation** - Choose paths through procedurally generated sectors\n3. **Combat Encounters** - Turn-based card battles against Void entities\n4. **Rewards** - Gain new cards, artifacts, or currency after victories\n5. **Events** - Story moments with meaningful choices\n6. **Boss Battles** - Challenging encounters at sector end\n7. **Death or Victory** - Permadeath with meta-progression unlocks\n\n### What Makes Us Different\n\n- **Void Corruption System**: Cards can become corrupted, gaining power but at a cost\n- **Memory Synergies**: Cards remember being played together, forming bonds\n- **Dynamic Difficulty**: Game adapts to player skill over runs",
      "tags": ["design", "core-loop"],
